verbose_text: The normalized GABA+ levels were significantly lower in neonates than in children in both regions, regardless of the approach employed (Wat-ref, p < 0.001 and p = 0.001 for BG and cerebellum, respectively, Figure XREF_FIG C; Cr-ref, p < 0.001 and p = 0.001, respectively, Figure XREF_FIG D).
